text:
Pastor Sam Adeyemi to Buhari: ‘We have an unusual opportunity with #ENDSARS protests’ Tribune Online
Pastor Sam Adeyemi to Buhari: &#8216;We have an unusual opportunity with #ENDSARS protests&#8217;

Lending his voice to the unabating EndSARS protests across Nigeria, popular Lagos preacher, Pastor Sam Adeyemi, on Tuesday said that the protests present an unusual opportunity to side with the youth and build Nigeria. Tweeting via his verified handle @sam_adeyemi, the clergyman and leadership expert wrote: &#8220;Our dear President of the Federal Republic of Nigeria, [&#8230;]
Pastor Sam Adeyemi to Buhari: &#8216;We have an unusual opportunity with #ENDSARS protests&#8217;
Tribune Online

